stories.title: Brian Vitori suspended from bowling for third time
stories.subTitle: Zimbabwe news
stories.seoTitle: Brian Vitori suspended from bowling for third time
stories.summary: The Zimbabwe seamer's action has been reported again, four matches after he was cleared to resume bowling following a 12-month ban

image.caption: Brian Vitori and Sikandar Raza rejoice at the fall of the final wicket

stories.title: We have to give 15 million people something to cheer about - Raza
stories.subTitle: Afghanistan v Zimbabwe, World Cup Qualifier, Group B
stories.seoTitle: We have to give 15 million people something to cheer about - Sikandar Raza
stories.summary: During their nail-biting victory against Afghanistan, Zimbabwe were lifted by the strong support from a huge crowd in Bulawayo, especially when their spirits were down

image.caption: Sikandar Raza made another important contribution
image.longCaption: Sikandar Raza made another important contribution, Zimbabwe v Afghanistan, Bulawayo, March 6, 2018

stories.title: Zimbabwe hang on to clinch two-run thriller
stories.subTitle: Zimbabwe v Afghanistan, World Cup Qualifier, Group B
stories.seoTitle: Zimbabwe hang on to clinch two-run thriller against Afghanistan
stories.summary: Afghanistan were cruising in their chase of 197 but then they collapsed, before their last wicket took them within touching distance of victory. But it wasn't to be.
